<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 10:09:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>新特拉维夫咖啡馆致力于治愈 10 月 7 日四分五裂的社区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/the-new-tel-aviv-cafes-looking-to-heal-communities-torn-apart-on-october-7/00000190-e06f-d566-adfa-eb6f5c910000</link><description>特拉维夫最新的连锁咖啡店 Café Otef 的每家分店均由疏散的基布兹成员经营并配备员工，所有收益都捐献给社区。 “你需要早上醒来并忙碌起来，这就是我们的孩子们现在看到的我们正在做的事情，”负责基布兹雷伊姆分部的罗伊特说</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 09:59:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/the-new-tel-aviv-cafes-looking-to-heal-communities-torn-apart-on-october-7/00000190-e06f-d566-adfa-eb6f5c910000</guid></item><item><title>报告：Nova 节幸存者讲述哈马斯恐怖分子如何在 10 月 7 日强奸他</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/report-nova-festival-survivor-recounts-how-hamas-terrorists-raped-him-on-october-7/00000190-e396-dab4-afb9-f3fe6cff0000</link><description>以色列第 12 频道的匿名报道与去年法国报纸上发表的报道一样 ■ 详细描述 10 月 7 日强奸事件的报道以及营救幸存者和第一个到达现场的人的证词浮出水面</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 09:38:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/report-nova-festival-survivor-recounts-how-hamas-terrorists-raped-him-on-october-7/00000190-e396-dab4-afb9-f3fe6cff0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡将就伊朗的侵略向国会发出警告。但他的伊朗政策却是一个巨大的失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-will-warn-congress-about-the-iranian-threat-his-iran-policy-has-been-disastrous/00000190-e00c-d2bf-a7f9-f0ff06130000</link><description>当以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡在国会演讲中提到伊朗时，鉴于他在这个问题上长达数十年的可怕、甚至是灾难性的记录，世界应该将其视为采取完全相反行动的信号</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 08:50:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-will-warn-congress-about-the-iranian-threat-his-iran-policy-has-been-disastrous/00000190-e00c-d2bf-a7f9-f0ff06130000</guid></item><item><title>“犹太人可以在圣殿山祈祷”：本格维尔颠覆以色列政策，而内塔尼亚胡在美国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/jews-can-pray-on-temple-mount-ben-gvir-upends-israeli-policy-while-netanyahu-in-u-s/00000190-e3d4-d548-a3ba-efde61200000</link><description>在题为“以色列重返圣殿山”的以色列议会会议上，本格维尔表示，“政治领导层允许犹太人在敏感地点进行祈祷”；联盟和反对派的议员们纷纷反对这一声明，其中一些人指责他试图煽动第三次起义，并要求解雇他</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 08:47:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/jews-can-pray-on-temple-mount-ben-gvir-upends-israeli-policy-while-netanyahu-in-u-s/00000190-e3d4-d548-a3ba-efde61200000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡将在人质家属的注视下向国会发表讲话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/hostage-families-fear-netanyahus-optimism-over-a-deal-is-to-help-him-survive-u-s-visit/00000190-e153-dbe5-a7fa-f77bccbf0000</link><description>接近以色列总理的消息人士称，他对国会的讲话将是和解的，他将赞扬拜登几十年来对以色列的支持</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 03:08:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/hostage-families-fear-netanyahus-optimism-over-a-deal-is-to-help-him-survive-u-s-visit/00000190-e153-dbe5-a7fa-f77bccbf0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列同意撤离250名加沙伤病员前往阿联酋接受治疗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-agrees-to-evacuate-250-sick-and-wounded-gazans-for-medical-treatment-in-uae/00000190-df16-d566-adfa-ff3605d10000</link><description>在高等法院就一项请愿书举行听证会之前，COGAT表示，以色列和世界卫生组织正在计划从埃拉特进行初步医疗后送，该请愿书要求建立一个从加沙疏散伤病员以获得必要医疗护理的系统</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 03:01:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-agrees-to-evacuate-250-sick-and-wounded-gazans-for-medical-treatment-in-uae/00000190-df16-d566-adfa-ff3605d10000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对被占领的美国的访问只不过是自恋的政治活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-visit-to-an-otherwise-occupied-america-is-nothing-but-narcissistic-politicking/00000190-e0fb-d566-adfa-ebfb9b150000</link><description>拜登承诺将利用其总统任期的最后几个月来确保加沙停火和人质返回，但即将卸任的总统将拥有多少精力还有待观察 ■ 据与内塔尼亚胡关系密切的人士透露，内塔尼亚胡并没有放弃人质协议 — — 或者与沙特阿拉伯的正常化协议 — — 但如果他确实选择达成协议，他仍然面临严重障碍</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 03:00:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-visit-to-an-otherwise-occupied-america-is-nothing-but-narcissistic-politicking/00000190-e0fb-d566-adfa-ebfb9b150000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军表示，它拦截了两架从东部向以色列发射的无人机；北部士兵受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article-live/security-source-masked-settlers-torch-palestinian-vehicles-in-w-bank-village-of-hawara/00000190-e281-d9bf-a195-e789725e0000</link><description>德国实施突袭并禁止被指控与伊朗、真主党有联系的组织 ■ 华盛顿邮报：以色列部长在阿布扎比会见阿联酋和美国代表，讨论战后加沙问题 ■ 两名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸的卡兰迪亚和图巴斯被以色列国防军枪杀，六人受伤 ■ 以色列国防军表示，从东部向以色列发射的两架无人机在一夜之间被成功拦截 ■ 白宫：拜登与内塔尼亚胡将于周四会面；特朗普定于周五在海湖庄园举行会议</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 02:20:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-24/ty-article-live/security-source-masked-settlers-torch-palestinian-vehicles-in-w-bank-village-of-hawara/00000190-e281-d9bf-a195-e789725e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡将于周四在白宫会见拜登，周五将在海湖庄园会见特朗普</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-to-meet-biden-at-white-house-on-thursday-trump-at-mar-a-lago-on-friday/00000190-e140-d9bf-a195-e5c841d80000</link><description>白宫确认，拜登总统将在以色列总理向国会发表讲话以及拜登向全国发表黄金时段讲话后不到 24 小时会见内塔尼亚胡，他将在讲话中首次阐述他不竞选连任的决定</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 20:53:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-to-meet-biden-at-white-house-on-thursday-trump-at-mar-a-lago-on-friday/00000190-e140-d9bf-a195-e5c841d80000</guid></item><item><title>议会为人力资源机构雇员提供免遭性骚扰的保护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/knesset-gives-protections-against-sexual-harassment-to-manpower-agency-employees/00000190-e11b-dab4-afb9-f37b83420000</link><description>该修正案还将禁止歧视性骚扰投诉者的规定扩大到通过此类机构雇用的工人</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 20:08:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/knesset-gives-protections-against-sexual-harassment-to-manpower-agency-employees/00000190-e11b-dab4-afb9-f37b83420000</guid></item><item><title>由于以色列总检察长拒绝上诉，2021 年骚乱中阿拉伯人被犹太人杀害的案件仍将结案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/case-of-arab-killed-by-jews-in-2021-riots-to-remain-closed-as-israels-ag-rejects-appeal/00000190-e107-d041-a3f4-e9eff21a0000</link><description>穆萨·哈苏纳的家人声称，此案的调查存在缺陷，是迫于政治压力而结束的。总检察长驳回上诉的决定并未解决这些主张</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 19:42:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/case-of-arab-killed-by-jews-in-2021-riots-to-remain-closed-as-israels-ag-rejects-appeal/00000190-e107-d041-a3f4-e9eff21a0000</guid></item><item><title>美国犹太人在哈里斯-夏皮罗选票中看到希望，同时准备迎接反犹太主义风暴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-23/ty-article/.highlight/american-jews-see-hope-in-harris-shapiro-ticket-while-bracing-for-an-antisemitic-storm/00000190-e04f-d2bf-a7f9-f0ff63e40000</link><description>在庆祝卡玛拉·哈里斯成为民主党推定提名人的同时，美国犹太人应该做好准备，迎接唐纳德·特朗普的基地将面临的坎坷之路。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 19:34:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-23/ty-article/.highlight/american-jews-see-hope-in-harris-shapiro-ticket-while-bracing-for-an-antisemitic-storm/00000190-e04f-d2bf-a7f9-f0ff63e40000</guid></item><item><title>教育部长表示，以色列与黎巴嫩边境附近的学校不会在秋季重新开放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/schools-near-israels-border-with-lebanon-wont-reopen-in-fall-education-minister-says/00000190-e0d0-d566-adfa-ebf213690000</link><description>教育部长约夫·基什在解释他九月份不重新开放北部社区学校的决定时告诉北部市长，“我们别无选择，只能决定对黎巴嫩发动一场激烈的战争”。自战争爆发以来，超过 16,000 名学生从北方撤离</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 19:10:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/schools-near-israels-border-with-lebanon-wont-reopen-in-fall-education-minister-says/00000190-e0d0-d566-adfa-ebf213690000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 291 天：内塔尼亚胡表示人质返回的条件“正在成熟”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-291-netanyahu-says-conditions-for-hostages-return-are-ripening/00000190-e04f-d548-a3ba-eecf4cd70001</link><description>世界卫生组织警告，由于健康和卫生条件不佳，加沙及其他地区小儿麻痹症爆发的风险很高。定居者 ■ 哈马斯和法塔赫称他们签署了宣言，誓言组建联合政府 ■ 战争开始 291 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 17:10:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-291-netanyahu-says-conditions-for-hostages-return-are-ripening/00000190-e04f-d548-a3ba-eecf4cd70001</guid></item><item><title>Einav Zangauker 发布了她的儿子 Matan 在加沙被囚禁的镜头以及他 10 月 7 日的短信</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/einav-zangauker-releases-footage-of-her-son-in-gaza-captivity-with-his-final-messages/00000190-e075-d9bf-a195-e5fdab440000</link><description>在视频中，马坦骑在汗尤尼斯的一辆摩托车上，背景中有人欢呼，这可能是在他被绑架后不久拍摄的。他给家人的最后信息显示没有警察在场，并恳求道：“军队什么时候来？”他们已经占领了一半的基布兹”</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 16:56:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/einav-zangauker-releases-footage-of-her-son-in-gaza-captivity-with-his-final-messages/00000190-e075-d9bf-a195-e5fdab440000</guid></item><item><title>世卫组织警告加沙及其边境地区的脊髓灰质炎风险很高，因为水卫生条件恶劣</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/who-warns-of-high-polio-risk-in-gaza-and-beyond-its-borders-amid-dire-water-sanitation/00000190-dfde-dab4-afb9-fffeebf10000</link><description>尽管在沿海飞地的污水样本中发现了这种病毒，但以色列军方表示，没有任何加沙居民感染这种疾病的信息；本周，以色列国防军开始为以色列士兵开展脊髓灰质炎疫苗接种活动</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 15:53:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/who-warns-of-high-polio-risk-in-gaza-and-beyond-its-borders-amid-dire-water-sanitation/00000190-dfde-dab4-afb9-fffeebf10000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其谴责以色列调频发布了埃尔多安婴儿时期躺在伊朗最高领袖腿上的人工智能图像</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/turkey-blasts-israeli-fm-for-ai-image-of-erdogan-as-baby-on-lap-of-iran-supreme-leader/00000190-dfb8-dbe5-a7fa-fffa967e0000</link><description>外交部之间的相互争执标志着土以关系持续恶化的又一步，这种关系十多年前就开始紧张，自加沙战争爆发以来迅速恶化</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 15:27:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/turkey-blasts-israeli-fm-for-ai-image-of-erdogan-as-baby-on-lap-of-iran-supreme-leader/00000190-dfb8-dbe5-a7fa-fffa967e0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯、法塔赫在华签署巴勒斯坦“团结”协议，无实际意义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/hamas-fatah-sign-palestinian-unity-agreement-in-china-with-no-practical-significance/00000190-df7d-d851-afbe-df7d78fa0000</link><description>消息人士称，巴勒斯坦各派就合作达成了总体谅解，并接受巴解组织作为组建巴勒斯坦民族政府的行政框架，但法塔赫高级官员表示，联合声明主要是为了表达对东道主中国的尊重</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 14:18:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/hamas-fatah-sign-palestinian-unity-agreement-in-china-with-no-practical-significance/00000190-df7d-d851-afbe-df7d78fa0000</guid></item><item><title>向国会发表讲话是内塔尼亚胡个人的胜利，也是以色列的又一次失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/why-netanyahus-congress-speech-will-be-an-even-bigger-failure-than-all-his-previous-ones/00000190-df64-d566-adfa-ff6661730000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡向国会发表空洞、失败、疏远的演讲的悠久历史</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 13:46:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/why-netanyahus-congress-speech-will-be-an-even-bigger-failure-than-all-his-previous-ones/00000190-df64-d566-adfa-ff6661730000</guid></item><item><title>拜登已将以色列制裁精灵从瓶子里放出来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/biden-has-let-the-israel-sanctions-genie-out-of-the-bottle/00000190-dfb1-dbe5-a7fa-fffbfbc50000</link><description>随着加沙战争的继续，越来越多的国家正在实施这些措施，而且该清单的规模可能会扩大到可能损害以色列经济的程度</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 13:37:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/biden-has-let-the-israel-sanctions-genie-out-of-the-bottle/00000190-dfb1-dbe5-a7fa-fffbfbc50000</guid></item></channel></rss>